      "id": "6c0a88e7_df4bc0de",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "message": "Thanks for your comment Cedric. The idea is to migrate to GHA. This workflow is just a \"comment-only\" workflow to make sure it works before we can actually migrate it. But the idea is to deprecate Jenkins and move to GHA. \nI wanna have the 2 running in parallel, (with only Jenkins voting for now) to assure they are reporting the same outcome.",
